snippet.title: Realm Royale - Closed Beta on PlayStation 4 & Xbox One
snippet.description: Realm Royale is coming to PlayStation 4 and Xbox One!  Choose your class and be the last champion standing in Realm Royale, the new battle royale game from Hi-Rez Studios!   Sign up for our closed beta today - key sign-ups are available now at http://www.RealmRoyale.com
